Drown

Arguably the most powerful single-combat spell known
to druidic lore, Drown is also one of the hardest to
master.  It was named for its apparent effect, but
it does not literally drown the target, as water-
breathing and even non-breathing creatures are
affected in the same manner.

Command: drown <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: Minimum 100, based on damage
Base Recovery: long
Base Effect: damage (extreme)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 25
